{"tid":553585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【知法犯法】休班警搭地鐵圖偷少女財物 隔一日落網走唔甩","createTime":"2018-02-07T15:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T03:39:03.000Z","uid":30647,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4989bfe606b894cbe77dd7c394367300172fc5f2","tid":553585,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:17:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>又有休班警員知法犯法！</strong></span> 昨日傍晚6時許，警員在進行反罪惡巡邏期間，於一列由金鐘開往尖沙嘴的列車上發現一名男子形迹可疑，打開附近一名16歲非華裔少女的背包，其後於港鐵尖沙嘴站逃去。警方今晨於觀塘區拘捕一名31歲姓梁男子，經調查後得悉他為一名休班警員，以涉嫌「企圖盜竊」將他拘捕。被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於二月下旬向警方報到，案件交由油尖警區重案組第一隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180207/57805465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57805465&d=voCK8FXwRRmMHUQ%2Fw2iICAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=6b4fdc1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57805465&h=03778a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180207/57805465</a>"},{"pid":"3f4b1e8c1124758ba9c47fc2e2ceac690bba0ac8","tid":553585,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"除左講恭"},{"pid":"539ca6eda0afbc3574b1d520f9d9d10ca2546038","tid":553585,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"休班警大熱，<br />\n休班輔警同當更警追唔到"},{"pid":"a0780981fcfb49f4b6976dc26a5c118587e7fa16","tid":553585,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"警方強非常注重⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"b40e6a588f4b51c40206de5dc89736f16a10dc11","tid":553585,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"入嚟為咗睇最後嗰段"},{"pid":"d44b19cbe87d7065694f183d90d3e5478a0c11f2","tid":55358